summary: So, there’s this scene in Captain Marvel where some dudebro basically gives her the “you should smile more” treatment and she...
body:
So, there’s this scene in Captain Marvel where some dudebro basically gives her the “you should smile more” treatment and she hurts and robs him. I’ve now seen people using that to prove that she’s a villain. Somehow.

I don’t know that I can entirely condone this action, if it was reality, but I confess I enjoyed watching it. But, anyway:

First, at the time she was a brainwashed amnesiac who believed she was an alien soldier. I can’t imagine blaming her for that action or thinking she was a villain because of it. Would she have done it as herself? Maybe. But, second point.

Of course, male heroes get away with such things all the time. Case in point, this is pretty much a nod to Terminator 2, and Arnold was never told he was a bad guy in that because, by the end, he wasn’t.

Come on, people, do better. You wear me out.

summary: People really need to stop acting like the petition to redo Season 8 of Game Of Thrones and the petition to replace Brie Larson...
body:
People really need to stop acting like the petition to redo Season 8 of Game Of Thrones and the petition to replace Brie Larson as Captain Marvel are the same.

The Game Of Thrones petition isn’t meant to actually happen, but instead to simply voice the opinions of fans who feel cheated and disrespected. It is to protest an ending that rushed and burned actual character development in order to get to the ending quicker, trampling over both fans, characters and stories alike rather than allowing a slow building development to give everyone the send off they were hoping for. And this is all because the writers were lazy, greedy and selfish leaving the fans with only one option of fighting back by voicing frustration for the very thing they all care about so deeply, to the point that some were in legit tears over the messiness of it all. At the current moment the petition also has over 1,559,606!

The Captain Marvel petition is piece of nonsense used by haters for nothing other than to shit on Brie simply because they don’t agree with her viewpoints. It has around 23,809 (and has been going much longer than the GOT one) and is a pathetic joke.
